page.title: 31Clothes shops in Havant
page.content:
There are quite a lot of clothes shops in Havant. New Look, cotton traders and more. Most of the clothes shops are new. There are some in and out of Havant town centre..

There are 10 and more to remember clothes shops altogether in Havant.

There is at least 1 men's clothes shop in Havant. Throughout Havant women have the most clothes shops. Sports Direct sells women's and men's clothes.
